  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
       <i class="fa-solid fa-people-carry-box"></i>
        <h2>How it works as a User?</h2>
        <h4>1. Sign in as a user</h4>
        <h4>2. Find the perfect bag for your trip</h4>
        <h4>3. Book it</h4>
        <h4>4. Pick it up</h4>
        <h4>5. Enjoy your trip</h4>
        <h4>6. Return it</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6">
       <i class="fa-solid fa-business-time"></i>
        <h2>How it works as an Owner?</h2>
        <h4>1. Sign in as an owner</h4>
        <h4>2. List you bag</h4>
        <h4>3. Wait for a reservation</h4>
